    title: "How an Ordinary Person Can Begin Rebuilding Themselves: A 30-Day Roadmap",
    description: "A simple route for stopping the bleeding, regaining structure, and starting a realistic rebuild of body, thought, and livelihood.",
    category: "Method",
    featured: false,
